creator: ComFreight
descriptionHtml:
Haul Pay is the payments app for trucking and logistics companies. Now you can make payment requests and sell your invoice digitally in real time, with no risk to you.

We also provide the ability to check credit approvals for current and potential customers, view your account history of advanced payments and more!

Our free tool also lets you create and share an invoice that's generated in seconds right from the app. Saves you a ton of time, headache and money now and in the future.

Haul Pay enables trucking and logistics companies to centralize and simplify their payments experience giving them total peace of mind.

Every time a user of Haul Pay requests payment via the Haul Pay payments program they are paid immediately upon delivery instead of having to wait days, weeks or months.

No more worrying about collections or juggling various requirements for various customers that you're moving freight for either.

Let us take it on for you.

Haul Pay >> We'll move you forward!
